title: Dimstar Promotions DP005: Alternative Bromley
description:
13 tracks from 13 independent, unsigned, cutting edge bands in the London borough of Bromley. The compilation covers genres from Rock, Metal, Alternative and Emo.

This album was originally a limited free sample CD that was given out at several live events throughout London. It was released in early August 2008. Included are all tracks @ 192kbs, ID3 tags and sleeve artwork.

www.dimstarpromotions.co.uk
